you're never going to know God's position

02:21:42.257 --> 02:21:44.479
until you've endured that and you have

02:21:44.520 --> 02:21:46.040
empathy for him in that regard.

02:21:46.740 --> 02:21:47.861
So I realized, okay,

02:21:47.881 --> 02:21:48.823
that's part of the job.

02:21:50.043 --> 02:21:51.164
It comes with the territory.

02:21:51.184 --> 02:21:53.386
It's a necessary part of the territory.

02:21:54.727 --> 02:21:56.308
But then there's the other part of it

02:21:56.327 --> 02:21:56.988
that says,

02:21:58.750 --> 02:22:00.031
if you're going to do this job and

02:22:00.050 --> 02:22:01.631
you realize that no one has ever done

02:22:01.672 --> 02:22:04.093
this job that has come out unscathed,

02:22:05.054 --> 02:22:07.575
everyone that speaks for Yahowah is hated.

02:22:08.594 --> 02:22:09.614
And so you're going to be hated.

02:22:10.555 --> 02:22:11.036
Deal with it.

02:22:13.515 --> 02:22:15.217
The proof statement here is getting

02:22:15.256 --> 02:22:17.176
through the gauntlet, being hated,

02:22:17.897 --> 02:22:20.257
having ninety nine point nine nine nine

02:22:20.317 --> 02:22:21.878
percent of people disparage you.

02:22:23.879 --> 02:22:24.779
If you can't take that,

02:22:24.838 --> 02:22:26.078
then you're the wrong guy for the job.

02:22:27.239 --> 02:22:28.959
Because that's what it's going to be,

02:22:29.000 --> 02:22:30.700
because that's the way it has always been.

02:22:30.719 --> 02:22:32.220
That's what I've had to endure these last

02:22:32.261 --> 02:22:33.140
six thousand years.

02:22:33.761 --> 02:22:35.001
I picked you because I think you can

02:22:35.040 --> 02:22:35.521
do that.

02:22:36.262 --> 02:22:37.402
And so it's important to do it.

02:22:39.468 --> 02:22:40.689
And then I began to see it as

02:22:41.209 --> 02:22:41.889
so irrelevant,

02:22:41.950 --> 02:22:44.211
it wasn't even worth mentioning anymore

02:22:45.111 --> 02:22:47.193
until I came to this.

02:22:48.155 --> 02:22:50.397
Same thing was true when we returned to

02:22:52.477 --> 02:22:53.379
Chawah's rebellion,

02:22:53.398 --> 02:22:55.421
which mirrors this in the creation

02:22:55.441 --> 02:22:55.700
account.

02:22:56.902 --> 02:22:57.541
And then here,

02:22:58.122 --> 02:23:00.043
and the reason that now I'm so pleased

02:23:00.064 --> 02:23:02.466
that we have done this is Yahowah is

02:23:02.505 --> 02:23:03.406
a really good teacher.

02:23:04.487 --> 02:23:08.170
He is sharing what he despises.

02:23:09.028 --> 02:23:10.091
So Leah just walked in.

02:23:10.171 --> 02:23:11.755
Is there instructions that you can give

02:23:11.775 --> 02:23:13.440
her that she can take the Good and

02:23:13.479 --> 02:23:15.284
Bad Woman song and send it to you

02:23:15.325 --> 02:23:16.888
in a way that you can post it?

02:23:18.536 --> 02:23:19.377
It's uploading now.

02:23:19.537 --> 02:23:20.257
It's uploading now.

02:23:20.458 --> 02:23:22.920
Unfortunately, it doesn't give us a bar.

02:23:22.979 --> 02:23:23.800
It just spins.

02:23:23.921 --> 02:23:26.423
So it shouldn't be two or three minutes.

02:23:26.643 --> 02:23:27.664
So keep talking.

02:23:27.744 --> 02:23:28.144
We'll get there.

02:23:28.203 --> 02:23:28.324
Well,

02:23:28.424 --> 02:23:29.706
I think we could probably do two or

02:23:29.726 --> 02:23:31.246
three minutes.

02:23:31.287 --> 02:23:32.868
I think we can manage that.

02:23:33.609 --> 02:23:34.709
I think we can probably manage that.

02:23:35.550 --> 02:23:39.513
And so by having God have these

02:23:39.554 --> 02:23:40.135
prophecies,

02:23:40.215 --> 02:23:44.257
one of the things that prophecy does two

02:23:44.298 --> 02:23:44.898
things for us.

02:23:46.211 --> 02:23:48.233
One is that it reveals that God knows

02:23:48.253 --> 02:23:50.213
what's going to happen long before it

02:23:50.254 --> 02:23:50.555
happens.

02:23:50.594 --> 02:23:53.316
He wrote these prophecies that depict this

02:23:53.355 --> 02:23:55.197
specific series of events with these

02:23:55.256 --> 02:23:58.099
particular people at this time doing these

02:23:58.138 --> 02:23:58.879
very things,

02:23:59.500 --> 02:24:01.060
two thousand seven hundred years ago.

02:24:01.161 --> 02:24:02.762
So now that when they happen,

02:24:03.301 --> 02:24:06.004
he is validating that his prophecy and his

02:24:06.064 --> 02:24:08.504
words through the prophet Yashayah are

02:24:08.565 --> 02:24:10.486
exacting and that we can trust him.

02:24:10.846 --> 02:24:11.506
And that's important.

02:24:12.843 --> 02:24:15.605
And the second is that a hundred percent

02:24:15.646 --> 02:24:18.128
of Yahowah's prophecies come with

02:24:18.167 --> 02:24:20.350
instructions.

02:24:20.709 --> 02:24:24.933
What God wants us to do is be

02:24:24.972 --> 02:24:27.995
observant so that we consider,

02:24:28.334 --> 02:24:34.260
we evaluate how he responds to things so

02:24:34.299 --> 02:24:36.601
that when we encounter such things,

02:24:37.102 --> 02:24:38.522
we can follow his example.

02:24:40.475 --> 02:24:42.415
And so the teaching and guidance here is

02:24:42.915 --> 02:24:44.835
when something like this occurs,

02:24:45.576 --> 02:24:47.816
you need to know this is my response

02:24:47.856 --> 02:24:48.156
to it.

02:24:48.297 --> 02:24:49.577
Don't be accommodating.

02:24:50.358 --> 02:24:52.118
Don't try to lure them back.

02:24:52.177 --> 02:24:53.279
Don't sweet talk them.

02:24:53.338 --> 02:24:55.058
Don't make accommodation for them.

02:24:55.119 --> 02:24:56.879
Don't not make excuses for them.

02:24:59.081 --> 02:25:00.261
Don't even ignore them.

02:25:01.960 --> 02:25:02.842
They're insidious.

02:25:03.602 --> 02:25:07.222
Go after them, condemn them, expose them.

02:25:09.570 --> 02:25:10.771
Do all of those things.

02:25:11.431 --> 02:25:12.811
And that's God's example.

02:25:13.572 --> 02:25:14.012
And, you know,

02:25:14.072 --> 02:25:16.712
I don't think we can ever go wrong

02:25:16.753 --> 02:25:20.352
to follow Yahowah's example.

02:25:20.393 --> 02:25:23.193
So those are the reasons why I find

02:25:23.273 --> 02:25:24.834
this refreshing.

02:25:25.574 --> 02:25:27.014
I find it uplifting.

02:25:27.094 --> 02:25:32.015
I find it affirming.

02:25:32.136 --> 02:25:34.036
I think our good friend and family member,

02:25:34.056 --> 02:25:34.495
Shannon,

02:25:34.656 --> 02:25:37.676
can make you a special shirt that says,

02:25:39.155 --> 02:25:41.516
I am impervious.

02:25:41.637 --> 02:25:42.277
I am impervious.

02:25:42.337 --> 02:25:43.838
Well, that is true.

02:25:43.918 --> 02:25:44.679
I am impervious.

02:25:45.799 --> 02:25:48.262
I have had more death threats probably

02:25:48.281 --> 02:25:51.543
than anyone alive, and I've never ducked.

02:25:53.084 --> 02:25:55.467
I've had DIY support from day one.

02:25:56.027 --> 02:25:58.908
We have written thirty five books

02:25:58.929 --> 02:25:59.408
together.

02:25:59.549 --> 02:26:02.470
We have delivered ten thousand profoundly

02:26:02.511 --> 02:26:03.592
important insights.

02:26:05.212 --> 02:26:05.654
We have

02:26:06.564 --> 02:26:08.064
done things that no one has ever done

02:26:08.103 --> 02:26:08.424
before.

02:26:08.444 --> 02:26:13.245
We've discovered the greatest truths in

02:26:13.306 --> 02:26:15.147
human history and shared them and

02:26:15.186 --> 02:26:15.826
delivered them.

02:26:15.887 --> 02:26:17.606
And we've done all of these things

02:26:17.647 --> 02:26:18.028
together.

02:26:18.987 --> 02:26:22.929
And he has always worked collaboratively

02:26:23.408 --> 02:26:24.069
supporting me,

02:26:25.250 --> 02:26:28.111
supporting us in this endeavor.

02:26:28.570 --> 02:26:31.652
And he is a marvelous father in the

02:26:31.691 --> 02:26:34.393
sense that he prefers to share credit than

02:26:34.452 --> 02:26:34.952
take credit.

02:26:36.690 --> 02:26:38.011
So no,

02:26:38.810 --> 02:26:42.233
I'm unfazed by it at this point,

02:26:43.333 --> 02:26:45.254
but I'm not gonna run from it either

02:26:45.314 --> 02:26:48.034
because again,

02:26:48.075 --> 02:26:52.236
the best example in the universe isn't

02:26:52.316 --> 02:26:54.917
actually Dowd's, it's Yahowah's.

02:26:56.259 --> 02:26:58.420
And when he takes a stand on something,

02:26:59.239 --> 02:27:00.140
we ought to learn from it.

02:27:00.460 --> 02:27:03.162
What was it that really annoyed him and

02:27:03.182 --> 02:27:05.143
what did he do and say in response

02:27:05.183 --> 02:27:05.423
to it?

02:27:06.819 --> 02:27:07.900
Did he turn the other cheek?

02:27:08.980 --> 02:27:09.140
No.

02:27:09.822 --> 02:27:10.682
Was he judgmental?

02:27:11.162 --> 02:27:11.782
Absolutely.

02:27:13.343 --> 02:27:14.144
Was he condemning?

02:27:14.263 --> 02:27:14.744
You betcha.

02:27:14.763 --> 02:27:15.444
Was he tolerant?

02:27:16.684 --> 02:27:19.066
No.

02:27:19.086 --> 02:27:20.527
So it's pretty clear what God has to

02:27:20.547 --> 02:27:24.129
think about this and the issues that are

02:27:24.209 --> 02:27:26.810
here and betrayal, sorcery,

02:27:28.111 --> 02:27:30.433
associating oneself with the demonic

02:27:30.472 --> 02:27:32.314
spirits, misrepresenting him,

02:27:32.373 --> 02:27:32.994
betraying him.

02:27:34.795 --> 02:27:37.376
Betraying what you knew to be true to

02:27:39.076 --> 02:27:44.898
garner a cadre of sycophants?

02:27:45.379 --> 02:27:47.399
No, God's not into that.

02:27:48.769 --> 02:27:49.068
All right,

02:27:49.129 --> 02:27:51.393
I think we have the song and let's

02:27:51.433 --> 02:27:52.254
go ahead and play it.

02:27:52.293 --> 02:27:55.337
And I bid you guys a wonderful rest

02:27:55.378 --> 02:27:56.218
of your Shabbat.

02:27:56.719 --> 02:27:58.381
This has been a great participatory

02:27:58.422 --> 02:27:58.903
program.

02:27:59.202 --> 02:28:03.087
I thank you a lot for doing so.

02:28:03.449 --> 02:28:04.911
So King of the Cables,

02:28:04.931 --> 02:28:05.752
can you play it for us?

02:28:39.041 --> 02:28:39.962
Nice.

02:28:40.724 --> 02:28:47.290
It looks like somebody read this chapter.

02:28:47.310 --> 02:28:49.573
Looks like somebody likes what Yahowah

02:28:49.612 --> 02:28:51.114
revealed through Yashayah.

02:28:51.174 --> 02:28:54.077
I see a lot of this chapter Yahowah

02:28:54.138 --> 02:28:56.280
has revealed in those words.

02:28:56.319 --> 02:28:56.880
How about you?

02:28:58.439 --> 02:28:59.738
She's pretty good at that.

02:28:59.759 --> 02:28:59.838
Yeah.

02:28:59.859 --> 02:29:00.099
You know,

02:29:00.158 --> 02:29:01.420
if you're going to plagiarize somebody,

02:29:01.979 --> 02:29:04.120
you might as well plagiarize God.

02:29:04.139 --> 02:29:07.661
That works out really well for you, too.

02:29:07.900 --> 02:29:09.002
He's happy about it, too.

02:29:09.022 --> 02:29:10.902
Go ahead.

02:29:10.922 --> 02:29:11.801
Go for it.

02:29:11.822 --> 02:29:12.462
Oh, my.

02:29:12.602 --> 02:29:13.323
That was lovely.

02:29:13.403 --> 02:29:16.424
I know you have her hovering over end

02:29:16.484 --> 02:29:16.863
episode.

02:29:16.884 --> 02:29:17.804
Can we just play that one more time?

02:29:50.663 --> 02:29:51.463
Choose wisely.

02:29:52.885 --> 02:29:54.206
Good night to one and all.

02:29:54.666 --> 02:29:59.191
Kevin, Kirk, my good friend, Dr. Jeff,

02:29:59.351 --> 02:30:02.393
and king of the cables over here, Rich.

02:30:02.894 --> 02:30:04.915
Thank you so much for being part of

02:30:04.956 --> 02:30:07.118
this marvelous contribution to Yahowah's

02:30:07.138 --> 02:30:07.278
family.

02:30:07.317 --> 02:30:07.597
Thank you, Rich.

02:30:07.618 --> 02:30:07.858
Good night.

02:30:07.878 --> 02:30:09.218
Thank you, Rich.

02:30:09.259 --> 02:30:10.299
Good night, Yahowah.